00:00:33.940 --> 00:00:40.860
The Biscuit Cuillere
Allows to make 2 round cake 20 cm &amp; 18 cm.
100 g flour
120 g egg white
80 g yolks
100 g flour
100 sugar , pinch of salt

00:00:57.240 --> 00:01:05.400
Mascarpone mousse
225  gr cream 
150 gr mascarpone cheese
2  egg-yolks

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.440
for syrup
25 ml water
1/2 vanilla bean 
60 gr sugar

00:01:16.100 --> 00:01:18.100
3 g gelatin

00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:27.880
80 ml espresso coffee, 40 gr sugar and 1 tbsp orange blossom water

00:01:39.480 --> 00:01:45.800
Beat the egg-whites with a pinch of salt , then add the sugar slowly , peaks keep beating in order to get a meringue.

00:02:19.600 --> 00:02:24.600
add the egg yolks and flour , mix delicately until homogeneous

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:47.960
Divide this mixture in 2 and spread it over 2 baking paper sheets, 2 round 20 cm and 18 cm

00:03:17.740 --> 00:03:21.760
sprinkle with icing sugar . 
Put in preheated oven 180 °  for 12 minutes .

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:33.560
Then leave to cool

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:41.740
Place the sugar , water  and vanilla bean in a sauce-pan.  cook the sugar until its temperature reaches 115°

00:03:47.740 --> 00:03:52.620
Start beating the egg yolks with a whisk

00:03:56.100 --> 00:04:00.000
Then pour the syrup  over the yolks whipping

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:02.445
Beat until the mixture is completely cooled

00:04:04.262 --> 00:04:06.262
Hydrate the gelatin in cold water.

00:04:06.540 --> 00:04:10.260
Soften the mascarpone

00:04:11.940 --> 00:04:14.980
Place a previous mixture in the mascarpone and  blend delicately until homogeneous

00:04:19.728 --> 00:04:26.788
Put a little of cream in a bowl , add the gelatin dissolved, then pour it in the mascarpone, egg yolks mixture and mix delicately

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:07.620
Whip the cold cream  in a bowl until it doubles its volume

00:05:09.040 --> 00:05:13.820
Then add it into the mascarpone mixture, mix delicately until homogeneous

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:51.000
Line a cake pan ( 20 cm) with Rhodoïd .
then put one biscuit cuillère in the bottom

00:06:17.740 --> 00:06:23.600
Brush with the coffee ,cover with a layer of mascarpone cream

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:45.920
Add the second biscuit cuillère  ( 18 cm) , brush it with the coffee

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:56.580
Add the rest of the cream, you can just spread it with a spatula or you can use a pastry bag with the tip you want, Refrigerate for a few hours or 1 hour in the freezer

00:07:25.620 --> 00:07:27.620
Sprinkle with cocoa powder. Remove the cake cercle, the rhodoid  and reserve in the fridge until service.

00:07:55.840 --> 00:07:57.840
thanks for your watching

